        "content": "<p>When <code>simp?</code> has a <code>config</code> argument, comments following <code>simp</code> are included in the suggestion <em>before</em> the <code>only [...]</code> part: (<a href=\"https://live.lean-lang.org/#code=import%20Std%0A%0Aexample%20%3A%20True%20%3A%3D%20by%0A%20%20simp%3F%20(config%20%3A%3D%20%7Bdsimp%20%3A%3D%20false%7D)%0A%20%20--%20a%20comment.%0A%20%20--%20another%20comment.%0A\">link to live code</a>)</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Std</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"bp\">?</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">config</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">dsimp</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">false</span><span class=\"o\">})</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- a comment.</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- another comment.</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\">/-</span><span class=\"cm\"> With suggestion clicked: -/</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">config</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">dsimp</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">false</span> <span class=\"o\">})</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">-- a comment.</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\">-- another comment. only</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- a comment.</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- another comment.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This results in the comment being duplicated with increasing indentation each line, and in the <code>only</code> being part of the comment.</p>",
